data.text: Federica Maria Mogherini (born 3 March, 549AER) is a Falleen politician, Member of Parliament and Chairwoman of the Democratic Unionist Party. Prior to this, she served as a Senator for the state of Darpartryo from 571 until 575. Mogherini was elected Democratic Chair in 584AER shortly after that year's general election, and is recognised to be the main architect of the merger between the DLP and the FDCP to form the DUP.
